    <div class="reveal">
      <h3 class="font-display font-bold">Password protection</h3>
      <p class="mt-1.5 text-sm text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed">Lock any link. Visitors authenticate before they get redirected.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="reveal">
      <h3 class="font-display font-bold">Expiry dates</h3>
      <p class="mt-1.5 text-sm text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed">Links that self-destruct. Set a date or let them live forever.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="reveal">
      <h3 class="font-display font-bold">Click limits</h3>
      <p class="mt-1.5 text-sm text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed">Cap clicks at any number. The link expires when it&rsquo;s reached.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="reveal">
      <h3 class="font-display font-bold">Custom OG previews</h3>
      <p class="mt-1.5 text-sm text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed">Control the title, description, and image that show in social cards.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="reveal">
      <h3 class="font-display font-bold">QR codes</h3>
      <p class="mt-1.5 text-sm text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed">Print-ready SVG codes generated for every link, instantly.</p>
