      <h3 class="font-display font-bold">UTM parameters</h3>
      <p class="mt-1.5 text-sm text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed">Set source, medium, and campaign at creation. Appended on redirect, invisible in the short URL.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

